		<tr><td>
		<p><br>


Tight-lipped
<br>
and her pulse throbs like
<br>
the belly of a frog.
<br>
Her windpipe contracts;
<br>
her octopus mouth hovers.
<br>

<br>
His eyes pick the newspaper columns
<br>
like carrion crows at a carcass.
<br>
His ears inhale the gaslike silence
<br>
seeping across the floor.
<br>
Their toenails grow quietly.
<br>

<br>
</td>
<td align="right"><img src="images/portraitold.gif">
<div class="artistline">Pat Jones</div>
